clearedPhysicalSettlement.Doc: Specifies whether the swap resulting from physical settlement of the swaption transaction will clear through a clearing house. The meaning of Cleared Physical Settlement is defined in the 2006 ISDA Definitions, Section 15.2 (published in Supplement number 28).
clearedPhysicalSettlement.Name: clearedPhysicalSettlement

predeterminedClearingOrganizationPartyRe.Doc: A reference to the clearing organization (CCP, DCO) to which the trade should be cleared.
predeterminedClearingOrganizationPartyRe.Name: predeterminedClearingOrganizationPartyReference
